Global Donuts Market Insights
Donuts Market size was valued at USD 6.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 8.7 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.2% from 2024 to 2030.


Donuts Market Overview
The global donuts market is valued at approximately USD 15 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow steadily at a CAGR of 5.6% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is driven by increasing consumer demand for convenient, delicious, and diverse snack options. Key players in the market are innovating with product varieties such as vegan, gluten-free, and gourmet donuts, which appeal to health-conscious and niche consumer groups. The market is expanding due to the growing popularity of donut chains and online delivery services, making it easier for consumers to access their favorite donuts. North America dominates the market, followed by Europe, where traditional donut consumption is ingrained in local cultures.

